enhanced_by.reason: The keySet method relies on the composite maps added via addComposited, making it essential to have maps added before calling keySet.
Removing a map from the composite affects the keySet, so testing keySet should consider scenarios with and without specific maps.
Clearing the composite maps affects the keySet, so testing keySet should include scenarios before and after clearing.
Adding a key-value pair to any of the composite maps affects the keySet, so testing keySet should include scenarios with and without new entries.
